members.description: A domain specific healthcare simulated factory dataset for members

member_id.2021-02-08T16:44:50.224086: a unique id for the member

zipcodes.2021-02-08T16:44:50.881677: Only covering 14 states woth a distribution based on population density

prf_has_phone.2021-02-08T16:44:51.100743: If the person has a phone number on record.

prf_not_call.2021-02-08T16:44:51.160202: If the member has elected not to be called. Must have a phone number

prf_channel_pref.2021-02-08T16:44:51.217326: The channel through which the member can be contacted
prf_channel_pref.2021-02-08T16:44:51.337514: ensure that if prf_not_call is true the preference isn't by phone
prf_channel_pref.2021-02-08T16:44:51.397786: ensure if the member has no phone number the channel preference is not SMS or Phone

prf_service_only.2021-02-08T16:44:51.276258: If the member has elected to be contacted only for servicing purposes

clinical.2021-02-08T16:46:06.094049: a section of clinical data taken from the sample reseach dataset on Diabetes

cln_pregnancies.2021-02-08T16:46:06.270230: Adjustment to ensure no males are have a value

segment.2021-02-08T16:46:06.876425: The heathcare segment of the member with bias weighting

line_of_business.2021-02-08T16:46:07.133252: The line of business this segment is in

prf_has_email.2021-02-08T16:46:07.301790: If the member has an email address on record

email.2021-02-08T16:46:07.463771: trimming those with email address for over 60s from the persona emails

cln_icd_10_code.2021-02-08T16:46:07.624017: The ICD codes for flu vaccination, Z23 - charable vaccine, Z28 - refused vaccine

cln_cpt_code.2021-02-08T16:46:08.034076: The CPT codes for flu vaccination, Z23 - charable vaccine, Z28 - refused vaccine

cln_cpt_dt.2021-02-08T16:46:08.636173: if had a previous flu shot, a date between 300 and 600 days previous to today

pcp_tax_id.2021-02-08T16:46:11.265091: Taken from the sample healthcare practitioners, matches a city to a practitioner list

is_PCP_auto_assigned.2021-02-08T16:46:11.576641: if the PCP has been auto assigned with a 7/3 positive distribution
